description:
Integral Life Practice

Starter Kit 

This is audio and video guidance related to self-help, spirituality, psychology, shadow work, buddhism, nonduality, meditation, workout, Big Mind, AQAL, God and 42. 

You would probably have to read yourself into the framework of Ken Wilber and related Integral stuff in order to make use of this or to get what it's all about, to appreciate it.

For what I know, these files were originally seeded on demonoid, dispersed to different torrents or together, and they are again. They have also been seeded to elbitz.net 

I wanted to share it to a public tracker, for once. See how it goes ...



[Unfortunately some mp3 files differ a bit in crc checksum, maybe because of tags, so its not possible to seed them to all torrents at the same time, without trixing (junctions etc)]





edit, september 2008: i have been seeding for a few months now, then dropped off. it survived 2 weeks since then, with your help. nice to see. i may drop in again, when needed, but eventually i will probably go away, like offline, shelterless, boxless with a backpack and my mala. 


